	<h1 class="title">Mac 的性能被 VR 先驱鄙视了，所以苹果最近在忙什么？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/497022/small/497022.jpg?1456799915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马若飞 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-06 07:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23348/medium/23348.jpg?1457093030" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="23348" data-title="《Mac 的性能被 VR 先驱鄙视了，所以苹果最近在忙什么？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23348/medium/23348.jpg?1457093030" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23348.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
